Data analysis: Each benchmark manuscript reports one or more F-measures for each software method. Due to the high variance of F-measures between studies (see Fig. 2C and Fig. S3 for a comparison), we renormalised the F-measures using the following formula: \documentclass[12pt]{minimal}
